Type:
DateTimeType, simple content
eAirway.10 Date/Time Decision to Manage the Patient with an Invasive Airway No No The date and time the decision was made to manage the patient's airway with an invasive airway device. Optional Airway DateTime consists of finite-length characters of the form: yyyy '-' mm '-' dd 'T' hh ':' mm ':' ss ('.' s+)?
